<item>
            <title>[LU-1808] Lustre build does not support FC15.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1808</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Lustre build does not support FC15.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;They are no target files as a starting point so if distro is fc15 the code in build/funcs.sh dies.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Failed build info is here:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master-fc15/6/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master-fc15/6/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please ask if you want any assistance testing under lbuild which is what Jenkins uses.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
